    "English": "Inserts a powerful field ionization device into the barrel of the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Boltcaster</span>, increasing projectile stability through the air.<br><br>Improves <span class=\"name name-stellar\">device accuracy</span> and allows the user to fire for longer periods without degrading combat performance.",
